= Introduction =

A list of variables for Lab2

= Variables for Lab2Main() =

 * sFile
   * sFile is the incoming source file from the user. This file is PRESERVED. sFile is passed to pass1 as a paramter

 * p1File
   * p1File a modified version of the incoming source file sFile. This file is returned from the pass1 object. This file is then consumed as a parameter by pass2.

 * p2File
   * p2File is a modified version of p1File. This file is returned from the pass2 object. This file is the final output.
